data.enText: fish and sea creatures that can be eaten, especially shellfish

tr: edible fish (broadly including freshwater fish) or shellfish or roe etc

value.def: Seafood is shellfish such as lobsters, mussels, and crabs, and sometimes other sea creatures that you can eat.

trans: 建兴酒家；建兴海鲜；建兴酒店
海鲜汤；海鲜浓汤；海鮮湯；希腊海鲜汤
